Package org.apache.fop.fo.extensions.svg

SVG extension classes which handle elements from the SVG namespace.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
BatikExtensionElementMapping This Element Mapping is for Batik SVG Extension elements of the http://xml.apache.org/batik/ext namespace.
SVGDOMContentHandlerFactory ContentHandlerFactory which constructs ContentHandlers that build SVG DOM Documents.
SVGElement Class representing the SVG root element for constructing an SVG document.
SVGElement.PDFUnitContext This class is the default context for a particular element.
SVGElementMapping Setup the SVG element mapping.
SVGObj Class for SVG element objects.
